      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHAMROCK HAYZE (1) was a (29.62) winner last time out at Q Parklands from Box 6. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with five wins from seven starts. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. GIVE ME BUCKS (2) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from 10 starts. Recorded a 2.5 lengths win (18.79) in a Grade 4 last time at Q Straight. Looks one of the chances. VALIDATE (4) generally flies the lids but last time was always well back and ran below best, finishing eighth (25.90) in a NG at Grafton. Prior to that was quickly into stride and scored (25.90) at Grafton. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won 11 of 19 tries. Boasts five wins from five starts out of this box. Can figure in the finish. SHOUT OUT SHAZAM (5) had won two starts on end leading into the last outing when strongly fancied but could only manage fifth (26.11) at this track. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong.",
